### Kinship Thresholds (reference)

| Relationship | Kinship Range |
|-------------|---------------|
| Duplicate / MZ twin | > 0.354 |
| 1st degree (parent-child, full sibling) | 0.177 – 0.354 |
| 2nd degree (half-sibling, grandparent) | 0.0884 – 0.177 |
| 3rd degree (1st cousin) | 0.0442 – 0.0884 |
| Unrelated | < 0.0442 |

