## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| O(N²) memory for large cohorts | OOM crash | Block-based computation, memory guard |
| O(N² × M) compute time | Very slow | Threshold-based pruning, recommend plink2 for >50K |
| Numerical precision | Test failures | Tolerance-based comparison |

